        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">You don't need OXYPHENBUTAZONE to score big. A <span class="text-white font-medium">7-letter bingo on a triple-word square</span> routinely scores 100-200 points in real games. Focus on bingo stems + premium square awareness, and 100+ turn scores become achievable.</p>
      </div>

